title: Starts of the Week + Week 7 Breakdown, Hot Potato - Fantasy Football Podcast for 10/20
description:
Week 7 is here!! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Starts of the Week and lots of Week 7 matchup previews! Plus, injury updates, a new edition of “Never Not Working,” and the Boom Boom Kicker! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for October 20th, 2022.
